051","tid":359964,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"幾點上庭？"},{"pid":"a3bcaf7dff460f44af10156c8d772431e54cbbc4","tid":359964,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:04:26.000Z","msg":"我返緊工<br />\n米屈"},{"pid":"3b12084920c12066db70616a3d69ed1382d25aed","tid":359964,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我返緊工<br />\n米屈</blockquote><br />\n鄭松泰聘鄭錦滿　若DQ齊齊失業<br />\n立法會議員都偏好聘用自己黨友做助理，不止建制及泛民如此，熱血公民議員鄭松泰亦不例外。根據鄭松泰所提交的議員申領開支表顯示，由去年10月份開始，他即聘用人稱「四眼哥哥」、該黨副主席鄭錦滿做地區辦事處主任，月薪1.5萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n四眼哥哥今年3月底因佔領行動期間違反禁制令，阻撓旺角清場而被法庭判監3個月，5月底才出獄，所以這幾個月都沒有糧出。不過，鄭松泰正面臨褫奪議員資格的官司，如果最終被取消資格，兩人就沒得撈了！"},{"pid":"034ffbd42a7903bde3e67c7dc7b582ba3cab68fa","tid":359964,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CHING上庭要唔要即討PO</blockquote><br />\n推我個post"},{"pid":"4c111c0d9e904753572abfa3c2f52c33e08b2fc9","tid":359964,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CHING上庭要唔要即討PO</blockquote><br />\n推我個post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d2b3718a8e679d7c9240274c21acea0542a489","tid":359964,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CHING上庭要唔要即討PO</blockquote><br />\n推我個post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}